data.name: Depot Deli and Lounge
data.description: Inspired by the everyday family cooking that we grew up with, you’ll feel at home while savoring a great meal in our casual and relaxed dining room in a restored Railroad Depot.  Experience our attentive service, Micro Brewed Beer, and friendly unique atmosphere; come see what makes us one of the most popular restaurants not only in Shenandoah, Iowa but also regionally.  Your headquarters for The Wabash Trace Nature Trail, Everly Brothers Memorabilia, local history and great food.  Established in 1983.
